OL,3,CCalls for more to be done to achieve
OL,4,Cgoal of a million Welsh speakers by
OL,5,C2050
OL,7,FThere are calls for the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment to do more to achieve their
OL,9,Fgoal of a million Welsh speakers by
OL,10,F2050.
OL,12,FIn 2017, the Welsh Government set a
OL,13,Fstrategic target for the number of
OL,14,FWelsh speakers to reach one million by
OL,15,F2050.
OL,17,FBut in the last census the number fell
OL,18,Fto 538,300, just 17.8% of people in
OL,19,FWales.
