OL,7,FAt the National Eisteddfod in
OL,8,FPontypridd, Plaid Cymru says a lack of
OL,9,Fschools is a key factor, with only two
OL,10,FWelsh-medium schools opened in the
OL,11,Flast three years.
OL,13,FOne parent calling for a secondary
OL,14,Fschool in Merthyr said: "If you speak
OL,15,FWelsh in Merthyr or want your children
OL,16,Fto have Welsh-medium education, you
OL,17,Fhave to make a sacrifice
OL,18,Funfortunately. You have to take your
OL,19,Fchildren out of their own community."
