OL,7,FAnother said: "As a community in
OL,8,FMerthyr, parents have to make that
OL,9,Fchoice really early on. Even when they
OL,10,Fare two that they know there is no
OL,11,Fprovision when they are 11, 12 years
OL,12,Fold.
OL,14,F"And they have to get on buses and
OL,15,Fhave to travel a little bit further
OL,16,Fand that has an impact then on the
OL,17,Fprovision that is there for the
OL,18,Fprimary school."
