OL,7,FOne pupil said: "I get a minibus from
OL,8,Fthe top of my street to the next
OL,9,Fvillage, Pant, and then I get a big
OL,10,Fcoach to Rhydywaun then. It is pain."
OL,12,FThe group launched a petition to call
OL,13,Ffor additional Welsh language support.
