OL,3,CCalls for more to be done to achieve
OL,4,Cgoal of a million Welsh speakers by
OL,5,C2050
OL,7,FElin Maher, national director for
OL,8,FParents for Welsh Language Education,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Parents want to see that
OL,10,Fcontinuation from early years right
OL,11,Fthrough, they have it in English-
OL,12,Fmedium education. Why are we still not
OL,13,Fseeing that within Welsh-medium
OL,14,Feducation in Merthyr?
OL,16,F"So, having the secondary provision
OL,17,Fwith a close proximity to parents is
OL,18,Fessential, hence we need to see that
OL,19,Fas soon as we can."
