OL,7,FMerthyr Tydfil Council say there are
OL,8,Fambitions to expand Welsh-medium
OL,9,Feducation opportunities across the
OL,10,Fcounty which includes a current
OL,11,Ffeasibility study into secondary
OL,12,Fprovision.
OL,14,FElsewhere, there are questions over
OL,15,Fwhether the Welsh Government will meet
OL,16,Fits target of one million speakers by
OL,17,F2050.
