OL,3,CCalls for more to be done to achieve
OL,4,Cgoal of a million Welsh speakers by
OL,5,C2050
OL,7,FHeledd Fychan MS, of Plaid Cymru,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We see a number of local
OL,9,Fauthorities not meet the target of the
OL,10,Fnumber that should be receiving Welsh-
OL,11,Fmedium education at the moment.
OL,13,F"So there are so many barriers here in
OL,14,FWales in 2024 and Welsh Government
OL,15,Fneed to invest more in the Welsh
OL,16,Flanguage and prioritise that so that
OL,17,Feveryone has equity of opportunities
OL,18,Fto use and enjoy the langauge."
